{"tid":2199492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"油塘一家4口染疫 當中2人曾做全民檢測未有結果先確診","createTime":"2020-09-12T09:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T09:51:06.000Z","uid":5737,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"556373e66092a742fec54102db66c31828b72fe6","tid":2199492,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:04:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200912/OVFJC4GGI5E3NMX6GUABGWFMSQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200912%2FOVFJC4GGI5E3NMX6GUABGWFMSQ%2F&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=f03ca16d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200912%2FOVFJC4GGI5E3NMX6GUABGWFMSQ%2F&h=708fcffb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200912/OVFJC4GGI5E3NMX6GUABGWFMSQ/</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鄧萃雯參與全民檢測：健康跟政治掛鉤超荒謬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2199273\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2199273</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n回力鏢<br />\n<br />\n鄧萃雯留言：「昨天早上檢測，剛剛已收到檢測報告，效率超快，去之前我的朋友們和媽媽都告訴我，檢測過程鼻+喉嚨需時不足20秒，一點不辛苦，三個字形容～快靚正。重點係，<span class=\"red\">現在好安心而我也不會是帶病毒者去傳染其他人，愛香港首先要負上最基本的公民責任。</span> #想驗就去驗我聽自己個心講 #只要繼續做足防疫措施就更有信心不會被感染 #尤其看見那些新冠感染大國想驗都冇機會就更覺珍惜和感恩 #連自己的健康都要跟政治掛鉤真係超荒謬 #我驗又唔係逼其他人驗咁都要被批評自由何在」"},{"pid":"fd3b7d6ddb87fbaaa550dd456f0559e9d2d9bc4a","tid":2199492,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:04:55.000Z","msg":"又話好安全 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08533352059e37b656a09980c44f85ad290ef88","tid":2199492,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img sr